<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ya-ca-zi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ya-ca-zi" class="zg-link" title="牙擦仔">牙擦仔</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xie-hua-guo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xie-hua-guo" class="zg-link" title="谢骅国">谢骅国</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3840019" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">这话刘秀对王霸说过，李世民对萧瑀也说过。<br>前者上面K神<a href="//www.zhihu.com/people/59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171" data-hash="59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171" class="member_mention" data-tip="p$b$59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171">@Kaiser</a>已分析了，就是站队正确的榜样。<br>后者性多猜贰，刚忌太过，一生宦海浮沉终归不进圈子，最后被老板改谥曰“贞褊公”。<br>然后，就没有然后了。


</div>

</div>
</div>
